SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''

END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    ELSE [p].[Name]

    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'

    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Borrows] AS [b]
        WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__borrow_InventoryNumber_0) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]

    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]
WHERE [b].[InventoryNumber] = @__id_0

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]
INNER JOIN [Books] AS [b0] ON [b].[InventoryNumber] = [b0].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
LEFT JOIN [Persons] AS [p] ON [b1].[ReaderNumber] = [p].[ReaderNumber]

SELECT TOP(1) [b].[Title], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N'In'
    ELSE N'Borrowed'
END AS [Status], CASE
    WHEN [p].[ReaderNumber] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE [p].[Name]
END AS [Borrower], CASE
    WHEN [b1].[Id] IS NULL THEN N''
    ELSE CONVERT(varchar(100), [b1].[ReturnDate])
END AS [DueDate]
FROM [Books] AS [b]

LEFT JOIN [Borrows] AS [b1] ON [b0].[InventoryNumber] = [b1].[InventoryNumber]
